<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.2.4">
<l>panta ṇainta melviralāḷ pāvaitaṉ kāraṇattāl</l>
<l>venti ṟalē ṟēḻumveṉṟa vēntaṉ viripukaḻcēr</l>
<l>nantaṉ mainta ṉākavākum nampi namperumāṉ</l>
<l>entai tantai tamperumā ṉevvuḷ kiṭantāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The king who conquered seven mighty, virile bulls</l>
<l>For the sake of the maid with soft fingers who was bound in kinship,</l>
<l>The prince who appeared in order to be the son of Nanda with extended fame,</l>
<l>Our great lord, my father’s father’s great lord, he is the one who lies in Evvuḷ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
